snippet.title: The Thief, the Witch, the Toad & the Mushroom - Teaser
snippet.description:
You're curled up in front of the fire reading a folk tale on a cold winter's night. Something about it seems so familiar. Have you read this before?

This game will release on March 23rd, 2024. Wishlist on steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2233770/The_Thief_the_Witch_the_Toad_and_the_Mushroom/
